casebody.data:
Iyang Peter ODUOK, Petitioner,
v.
FULTON DEKALB HOSPITAL AUTHORITY, dba Grady Memorial Hospital, et al. No. 19-6435 Supreme Court of the United States. January 13, 2020

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Georgia dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
